dct_title_s: America with those known parts in that unknowne worlde both people and manner of buildings
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Matches item 2, dated 1626-7, in Tooley's California as an island (Map collector's circle, no. 8); Boston and Long Island not marked, [p.] 9-10 on verso. From: A prospect of the most famous parts of the world ... London, 1627. Includes text, inset of Greenland, col. ill. of native figures and town views in margins. Text of "The description of America" on verso.
dct_publisher_sm: [London] : Are to be sold in Pops-head Alley against the Exchange by G. Humble, [1626 or 1627]
